[[Depot Bravo Five]] was a [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] supply depot located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. In [[21 BBY/Legends|21 BBY]] it was the site of a [[Terrorist/Legends|terrorist]] [[Depot Bravo Five terrorist attack|attack]] during which fifteen [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] were [[Death/Legends|killed]]. The [[Coruscant Security Force/Legends|Coruscant Security Force]] investigated the incident.

